name: Big Blue, cuff
description:
Black steel wire, swirl and wind around a variety of subjects like large oval blue agate stones, vintage buttons, coloured glass beads, brightly coloured flowered beads, and other metallic accents.
This is a large cuff bracelet grows in width from 1" to 2". The fixture of the bracelet is built in and has 3 different closures to accomadates different sizes.

name: Blue agate floral pendant
description:
Black steel wire and a variety of brightly coloured beads including vintage buttons, blue agate and red and black coral, help to form a playful floral pendant that measures 2/12" width and long.
It is finished with a black, cable-link, nickle-free chain.

name: candy colour bracelet in brown wire
description: A variety of multi coloured beads and buttons make up this fun, whimsical bracelet that is created by hand in brown wire.

name: Fall green floral pendant
description: This large delicate floral inspired pendant that is made of glass beads, turquoise, coral and a natural seed. Brown coloured, copper based wire is used to create the piece. It is strung with three different kinds of nickle free gunmetal and copper coloured chains.

name: fall green earrings
description:
Coloured with rich and delicate greens and purples using turquoise as a central bead, these drop earrings hang nearly 2" long.
Created with a brown coloured copper base wire.
The earring findings are nickle-free.
